videos.headline: Illinois celebrates after beating Wisconsin to win Big Ten title
videos.description: Illinois defeats Wisconsin 93-87 to claim the Big Ten championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Illinois celebrates after beating Wisconsin to win Big Ten title) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: AJ Storr gets the steal and 3 for Wisconsin
videos.description: AJ Storr comes up with a steal, then knocks down a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (AJ Storr gets the steal and 3 for Wisconsin) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Terrence Shannon Jr. gets the layup to fall
videos.description: Terrence Shannon Jr. drives, then makes the layup to give Illinois the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Terrence Shannon Jr. gets the layup to fall) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dain Dainja's layup gives Illinois the lead
videos.description: Luke Goode sends an outlet pass to Dain Dainja who lays it in to give Illinois the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dain Dainja’s layup gives Illinois the lead) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Illinois goes up on Terrence Shannon Jr.'s trey
videos.description: Terrence Shannon Jr. knocks down a 3-pointer to give Illinois a 3-point lead.
